    "description": "Arabian Iranians of tribal lineage who initially migrated to Iran in the 13th and 14th century and intermixed with the indigenous population of older Arabic-speaking background. Sunni Muslim Arabs who settled on the Iranian coast and later remigrated back to the Arabian Peninsula.",
